          <span><strong>Audit documentation for insurers and regulators:</strong> Training completion records, staff acknowledgment forms, risk assessment templates, and compliance checklists that satisfy SRA, Law Society, and cyber insurance requirements.</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <div class="text-emerald-600 font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</div>
