    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-blue-900 mt-12 mb-5">The Cost of Compliance: Consultants vs. SMBCyberHub</h2>

    <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-8 mb-8">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
