      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-blue-900 mb-3">Built for Small Law Firms</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-700">The Pro Kit includes everything a small practice needs to demonstrate cybersecurity compliance: audit-ready training records, written security policies, an incident response plan, and risk assessment documentation — all deployable by your office manager in a single afternoon.</p>
