    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-blue-900 mt-12 mb-5">The Privacy Advantage for Law Firms</h2>

    <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-emerald-50 rounded-xl p-6 border-l-4 border-emerald-500 mb-8">
